-- Manchester United Defender Vidic Agrees to `Long-Term' Contract Extension
-- Christopher Elser
-- 2010-07-23T17:17:15Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-23/manchester-united-defender-vidic-agrees-to-long-term-contract-extension.html

          
          
             Manchester United defender Nemanja
Vidic agreed to a “long-term” contract extension with the
English Premier League club.  
 The player had agreed to the contract, which still needs to
be signed, several weeks ago after returning from the World Cup,
United Chief Executive Officer David Gill said today on the
team’s website.  
          
          


  


        